Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.87,0:00:09.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,压抑高昂的鼓动 奔向暮色昏暗的街道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:09.87,0:00:17.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真心和客套之间 对那傢伙的想法複杂交错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:17.51,0:00:21.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有答案也无妨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.25,0:00:28.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了这份爱粉身碎骨 你的表情为何如此寂寞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:28.16,0:00:35.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谎言心机嫉妒背叛 有如家常便饭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:35.73,0:00:39.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无须大惊小怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.44,0:00:43.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玻璃之心点燃火苗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:43.51,0:00:46.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多想再去见你一面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:46.74,0:00:50.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在不行动 何时才要做呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.51,0:00:54.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蔷薇花开 蔷薇花落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:54.55,0:00:57.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的心中有我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.62,0:01:03.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高雅的 优美的 华丽的飞舞吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.73,0:01:06.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蔷薇花开 蔷薇花飞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.76,0:01:09.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的眼中有你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.80,0:01:15.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用心祈祷的话一定能改变命运
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:15.94,0:01:18.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燃烧热情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:18.97,0:01:21.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活得灿烂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.98,0:01:26.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与你同在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:30.92,0:01:35.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第3话 北斗的继承者
