Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.68,0:01:55.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拳…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.65,0:02:00.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我如果死了\N一定会给你添麻烦的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.12,0:02:03.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我能做的\N就只有像个杀手一样低调的死去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.05,0:02:06.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,垃圾就该有垃圾的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.36,0:02:10.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永别了，拳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.14,0:02:23.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老李
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.21,0:02:30.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麽了吗？老李
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.58,0:02:34.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北大路…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.15,0:02:36.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麽了？发生什麽事了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.20,0:02:51.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北大路，这是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.13,0:02:52.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.20,0:02:55.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我带老爷爷进来后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.17,0:02:59.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,端茶回来时，他就不见人影了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.11,0:03:00.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还留下了这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.08,0:03:06.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拳，承蒙你的照顾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.05,0:03:11.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你让我回想起怀念的过往\N心中十分高兴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.45,0:03:13.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多保重了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.22,0:03:18.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老李，你想独自寻短吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.54,0:03:32.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等，老师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.84,0:03:38.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起，晚上才来找你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.98,0:03:42.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啵儿亮 啵儿亮 啾啾啾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.32,0:03:45.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的新车小宝贝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.45,0:03:48.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擦得亮晶晶 啵儿亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.83,0:03:52.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比我的光头还闪亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.30,0:03:59.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这麽晚了，学生还跟老师在一起\N你想要去哪裡？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.97,0:04:05.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没规矩，太没规矩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.68,0:04:10.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师，你要去哪裡？老师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.68,0:04:13.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个老爷爷到底是什麽人？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.48,0:04:18.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的，这跟妳没关係\N妳早点回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.12,0:04:21.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是，他看着我的脸叫玉玲…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.12,0:04:24.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他到底是什麽人？老师\N怎麽了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.23,0:04:26.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麽回事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.03,0:04:27.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.06,0:04:29.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你等一下，老师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.60,0:04:33.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别走，拳志郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.57,0:04:34.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玉玲…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.20,0:04:37.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.45,0:04:49.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉，让妳暂时睡一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.75,0:04:55.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绫小姐…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.93,0:04:59.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个下流教师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.33,0:05:02.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想对北大路家的千金做什麽！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.03,0:05:11.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霞老师，你终于现出原形了\N既然如此…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.68,0:05:16.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你来得正好，跟我来一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.95,0:05:19.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要打吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.65,0:05:23.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别看我这样\N我可是柔道二段，珠算八段的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.42,0:05:28.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.92,0:05:30.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想干嘛啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.40,0:05:43.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.64,0:05:46.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开车？遵命…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.25,0:05:54.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什麽是这样…\N谁来告诉我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.67,0:06:16.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你把他吊在这种地方想干嘛？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.97,0:06:21.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个老头会引来阎王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.24,0:06:22.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麽？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.94,0:06:25.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阎王的嗅觉像狗一样灵敏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.81,0:06:28.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想必他现在已经寻着\N老李的血腥味追来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.45,0:06:31.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此，真是好点子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.39,0:06:38.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金克荣\N你也想要阎王人头的悬赏金吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.13,0:06:39.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想怎样？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.56,0:06:41.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然是射杀阎王啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.96,0:06:44.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,50万赏金我要定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.30,0:06:48.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再厉害的拳法高手也敌不过手枪…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.01,0:06:51.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可不见得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.71,0:06:55.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拳法究竟斗不斗得过手枪…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.91,0:07:00.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要不要拿\N人称河北拳侠的我试试看啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.28,0:07:02.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这是什麽意思？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.22,0:07:05.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我的拳法能够打倒他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.42,0:07:08.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和那把枪都不是他的对手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.46,0:07:12.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混帐，你想独吞赏金吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.17,0:07:20.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麽嘛，比想像中温和多了\N这麽慢一定闪得过啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.00,0:07:24.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轻轻鬆鬆…\N这傢伙的八极拳只有这点程度啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.68,0:07:37.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是金克荣吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.42,0:07:41.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇帝的禁卫队队长为何要这麽做？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.56,0:07:44.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁都无法阻挠我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.03,0:07:47.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你难不成跟阎王有过节？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.86,0:07:51.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就让你看看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.84,0:07:58.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这道伤痕难道是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.17,0:08:03.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以前在上海\N当过犹太财阀的保镖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.58,0:08:06.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时曾经和阎王交手过一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.02,0:08:09.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我唯一一次和人打成平手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.65,0:08:13.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是当时留下的伤痕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.07,0:08:31.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这裡真是热闹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.61,0:08:34.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是繁华上海啊，这样才对嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.45,0:08:38.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想做什麽…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.82,0:08:45.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起跳支舞吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.80,0:09:06.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混账\N站住！你没听到吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.71,0:09:08.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这裡不是你这种人可以来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.08,0:09:15.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烦死了，老子有带女伴来耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.06,0:09:29.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.57,0:09:43.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是河北拳侠，金克荣吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.55,0:09:45.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说你是个高手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.11,0:09:47.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麽样？要不要跟我一较高下啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.15,0:09:49.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你滚吧，小子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.78,0:09:51.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我劝你珍惜自己的生命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.45,0:09:54.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珍惜生命？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.96,0:09:57.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拳法家才不在意那种小事呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.13,0:10:03.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当眼前出现了厉害的高手\N这时只需要决定谁强谁弱就够了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.74,0:10:16.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已经死了一次囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.68,0:10:20.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫什麽名字？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.02,0:10:23.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人们都叫我阎王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.10,0:10:35.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如他所说的一样…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.53,0:10:39.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我虽然是禁卫队队长\N却也是一名拳法家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.57,0:10:44.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一决胜负比什麽都重要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.14,0:10:45.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什麽要这麽执着？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.24,0:10:48.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为那小子…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.42,0:11:36.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在后来激烈的打斗中\N始终没有使出北斗神拳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.63,0:11:41.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拳从以前就是那样了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.96,0:11:48.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他总是封印北斗神拳\N不断追求属于自己的拳法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.14,0:11:52.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这对我来说是一种侮辱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.44,0:11:57.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除非打倒北斗神拳\N否则我的屈辱是无法洗刷的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.88,0:12:01.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早已置生死于度外了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.55,0:12:04.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要用拳法与他一决胜负
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.02,0:12:07.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.18,0:12:29.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金克荣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.88,0:12:31.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你杀了我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.88,0:12:35.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你用我的血腥味将阎王引诱来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.25,0:12:37.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经没有利用价值了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.99,0:12:46.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连人称睡龙的青帮首席用毒高手\N李永健都不敌衰老病痛吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.43,0:12:49.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来你也知道我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.96,0:12:54.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你也应该很清楚\N我没有活着的价值了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.80,0:13:01.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在你所淌的血\N对阎王有着强烈的引诱力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.31,0:13:09.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这点你儘管放心吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.98,0:13:12.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阎王已经快到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.85,0:13:16.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为他来了，你就可以逃脱吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.12,0:13:22.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是，我想请你削烂我的脸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.20,0:13:22.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什麽？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:23.10,0:13:29.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实大家都不知道\N红华会也有悬赏我的人头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.30,0:13:30.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又如何？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.70,0:13:35.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和阎王见面被很多人知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.48,0:13:40.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我死的话\N阎王的身份很可能会曝光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.81,0:13:42.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因为这点小事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.22,0:13:44.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死前先毁容埋名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.95,0:13:48.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我这个没用的老人\N能做的也只有这些了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.36,0:13:53.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你才想跳入水泥浆自杀吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.86,0:13:57.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阎王是我的朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.07,0:14:00.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.50,0:14:06.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他能让一个男人有这种决心\N这个阎王究竟是何方神圣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.44,0:14:10.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你，金克荣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.45,0:14:12.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我欠你一份人情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.58,0:14:18.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拳…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.47,0:14:38.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.84,0:14:43.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳终于醒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.74,0:14:48.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来的时候发现妳睡在门口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.12,0:14:51.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢妳，校长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.15,0:14:55.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我先告辞了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.12,0:14:57.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.97,0:15:10.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是怎麽了呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.97,0:15:12.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师把手放到我额头上后…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.01,0:15:14.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我突然就变得好睏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.34,0:15:21.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了，那个老爷爷和老师\N他们两个都叫我玉玲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.05,0:15:22.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玉玲？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.98,0:15:26.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来霞还记着这个名字…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.92,0:15:29.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲，你知道谁是玉玲吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.73,0:15:35.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了该和妳讲明白的时候了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.40,0:15:45.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.17,0:15:49.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玉玲是老师在上海时的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.94,0:15:53.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后妳指的老爷爷恐怕是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.58,0:15:59.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来之后会让妳难过了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.49,0:16:01.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会，只是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.92,0:16:06.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果可以的话\N我想再见老师一面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.49,0:16:08.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想见霞老师一面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.63,0:16:16.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老李，撑着点，千万别出事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.54,0:16:20.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.18,0:16:24.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.82,0:16:39.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什麽啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.70,0:16:46.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的新车为什麽要惨遭这种毒手…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.13,0:16:50.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,况且，我为什麽要开车载他啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.57,0:16:55.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶，我一定要逼他下车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.99,0:17:06.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玉玲…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.12,0:17:08.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛，你哭了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.16,0:17:14.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老李
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.57,0:17:26.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太突然了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.08,0:17:33.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什麽？告诉我，告诉我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.51,0:17:35.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什麽？为什麽？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.10,0:17:54.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.13,0:18:19.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老李
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.70,0:18:22.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老李
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.40,0:18:30.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要开心和朋友重逢还太早了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.80,0:18:35.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个铁扇…\N你是河北拳侠，金克荣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.21,0:18:38.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还记得我真是甚感荣幸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.75,0:18:39.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太卑鄙了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.35,0:18:43.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然拿老李当诱饵引诱我过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.02,0:18:49.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我哪裡卑鄙了 你忘记自己对我做过的事情了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.71,0:19:10.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那次死斗之后我一直在找你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.44,0:19:15.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后发现北斗神拳才是你的绝招
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.45,0:19:20.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拳法家对决时全力以赴是礼貌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.45,0:19:25.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而你在那时\N却始终都没有用北斗神拳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.81,0:19:47.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.49,0:20:05.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看，当时只留下这道伤痕\N而且还是被我自己的铁扇伤到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.63,0:20:07.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我一定要洗刷这份屈辱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.18,0:20:25.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碰到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.22,0:20:27.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.35,0:20:30.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不躲开\N会被我的掌底击穿心脏的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.19,0:20:33.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麽？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.00,0:20:36.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.13,0:20:39.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什麽？我为什麽动不了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.31,0:20:48.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他什麽时候出手的？\N我完全没有察觉到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.08,0:20:53.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他只是用手托住而已\N我就完全使不上力了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.41,0:20:57.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪，我怎么会起鸡皮疙瘩…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.85,0:21:00.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难不成我是在害怕他吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.35,0:21:01.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麽会…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.33,0:21:06.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他究竟是谁？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.86,0:21:07.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.86,0:21:10.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这跟我在上海对决过的男人\N简直完全不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.30,0:21:12.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.94,0:21:20.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金克荣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.37,0:21:23.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我为在上海时的无理道歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.04,0:21:26.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出身在北斗的世家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.75,0:21:28.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北斗神拳代代规定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:28.58,0:21:33.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了继承者之外\N和其他流派相斗时必须封印神拳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.82,0:21:40.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我当时还不是继承者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.79,0:21:45.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是一头盲目追求自己的拳法\N渴望鲜血的饿狼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.80,0:21:46.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那现在呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:49.64,0:21:55.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是第62代北斗神拳继承者\N霞拳志郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.68,0:22:04.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霞…拳志郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.55,0:22:09.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们全力以赴分个你死我活吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:15.60,0:22:18.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我动不了，完全动不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:19.17,0:22:20.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是他的斗志害的吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:21.03,0:22:24.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不，并不是我在害怕他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:25.37,0:22:28.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是我身为拳法家的本能在退却
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:28.44,0:22:31.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我的本能感受到死亡了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:33.08,0:22:34.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是不可能的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:35.01,0:22:38.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快给我动啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:38.25,0:22:40.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快动啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:50.46,0:22:52.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已经死了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.13,0:22:55.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麽了？这是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:01.57,0:23:03.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是北斗的死神吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:07.95,0:23:15.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已经死了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:15.32,0:23:18.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这句话…难道是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:18.62,0:23:21.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已经死了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:21.96,0:23:22.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:24.00,0:23:24.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:26.03,0:23:27.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:31.10,0:23:33.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动啊，我的身体快动啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:33.84,0:23:35.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点给我动啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:45.62,0:23:49.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个字，那句话，那个意思是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:49.56,0:23:50.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:01.40,0:24:04.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金克荣，你已经死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:07.57,0:24:10.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已经死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:24.76,0:24:27.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寂静安眠的城市中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:28.06,0:24:31.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不禁陷入深深沉思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:32.00,0:24:35.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然有许多琐碎的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:35.94,0:24:39.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却没错过妳瞬间的不安神情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:39.81,0:24:43.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我问妳是不是已经不再爱我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:43.78,0:24:49.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有答案就等于是答案了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:50.38,0:24:58.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算在那种时候与妳相遇了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:58.32,0:25:04.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会像被冰冻一般无法言语吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:05.26,0:25:06.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:06.93,0:25:11.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心跳好比四散的蝴蝶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:11.70,0:25:14.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变成微风与色彩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:14.81,0:25:19.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心跳爆裂飞散出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:22.72,0:25:30.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳有如蝴蝶从我心中远去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:30.26,0:25:40.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有妳 我的一切都将停摆
